OL,5, A sub-postmaster tried to take his own 
OL,6, life in the years after an IT glitch   
OL,7, led to him being falsely accused of    
OL,8, stealing money from his branch.        
OL,10,FMark Kelly, 43, ran the Brondeg Post   
OL,11,FOffice in Swansea from 2003 until 2006.
OL,13,FHe said: "It made me feel guilty and   
OL,14,Fdepressed. Over the years, I started   
OL,15,Fthen to blame myself and I tried to end
OL,16,Fmy life a few times."                  
OL,18,FThe Post Office said it was "sincerely 
OL,19,Fsorry" for how victims and their       
OL,20,Ffamilies had been affected.            
